<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>丰麒集团有限公司 | FENGQI GROUP</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Cinzel:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #C9A84C;
    --gold-light: #E8CC7A;
    --gold-dark: #8B6914;
    --black: #0A0A0A;
    --black-2: #111111;
    --black-3: #1A1A1A;
    --white: #F5F0E8;
    --white-dim: rgba(245,240,232,0.7);
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { background: var(--black); color: var(--white); font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif; overflow-x: hidden; cursor: none; }

  /* Cursor */
  .cursor { position: fixed; width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--gold); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 9999; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); }
  .cursor-ring { position: fixed; width: 36px; height: 36px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.5); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 9998; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); transition: all 0.15s ease; }

  /* Nav */
  nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000; padding: 24px 60px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; transition: all 0.4s ease; }
  nav.scrolled { background: rgba(10,10,10,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); padding: 16px 60px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); }
  .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-logo-icon { width: 42px; height: 42px; border: 1px solid var(--gold); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 16px; color: var(--gold); }
  .nav-logo-cn { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 4px; display: block; }
  .nav-logo-en { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 9px; color: var(--gold-dark); letter-spacing: 5px; display: block; margin-top: 2px; }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--white-dim); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 3px; position: relative; transition: color 0.3s; }
  .nav-links a::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); transform: scaleX(0); transition: transform 0.3s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .nav-links a:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

  /* Hero */
  .hero { height: 100vh; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 40%, rgba(201,168,76,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%), linear-gradient(180deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--black-2) 100%); }
  .hero-grid { position: absolute; inset: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 80px 80px; mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 80% at 50% 50%, black 30%, transparent 80%); }
  .hero-content { position: relative; text-align: center; z-index: 2; padding: 0 20px; }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 8px; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 28px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.3s forwards; }
  .hero-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif; font-size: clamp(52px, 8vw, 96px); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.5s forwards; }
  .hero-title span { color: var(--gold); }
  .hero-subtitle { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: clamp(12px, 2vw, 16px); letter-spacing: 10px; color: var(--gold-dark); margin-bottom: 48px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.7s forwards; }
  .hero-divider { width: 120px; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent); margin: 0 auto 40px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease 0.9s forwards; }
  .hero-tagline { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--white-dim); letter-spacing: 6px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 1s ease 1.1s forwards; }
  .hero-scroll { position: absolute; bottom: 40px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px; opacity: 0; animation: fadeIn 1s ease 1.8s forwards; }
  .hero-scroll span { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--gold-dark); }
  .scroll-line { width: 1px; height: 50px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold), transparent); animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .hero-corner { position: absolute; width: 60px; height: 60px; opacity: 0.4; }
  .hero-corner.tl { top: 20px; left: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--gold); border-left: 1px solid var(--gold); }
  .hero-corner.tr { top: 20px; right: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--gold); border-right: 1px solid var(--gold); }
  .hero-corner.bl { bottom: 20px; left: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); border-left: 1px solid var(--gold); }
  .hero-corner.br { bottom: 20px; right: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); border-right: 1px solid var(--gold); }

  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
  @keyframes scrollPulse { 0%,100% { opacity:0.3; } 50% { opacity:1; } }

  /* Section commons */
  .sec { padding: 120px 60px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .sec-bg { background: var(--black-2); border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08); }
  .sec-bg .sec { max-width: none; }
  .sec-bg-inner { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 120px 60px; }
  .section-label { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 6px; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .section-label::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 30px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); }
  .section-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .section-title em { color: var(--gold); font-style: normal; }
  .gold-line { width: 60px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 60px; }

  /* About */
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start; }
  .about-text { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 2; color: var(--white-dim); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .about-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); margin-top: 8px; }
  .stat-item { background: var(--black-2); padding: 28px 24px; transition: background 0.3s; }
  .stat-item:hover { background: var(--black-3); }
  .stat-number { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 44px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--white-dim); letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .about-card { background: var(--black-3); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); padding: 48px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .about-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 3px; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold), transparent); }
  .about-card-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 4px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .about-card-text { font-size: 14px; line-height: 2.2; color: var(--white-dim); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .honor-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--white-dim); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .honor-item::before { content: '◆'; color: var(--gold); font-size: 7px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px; }

  /* Segments */
  .segments-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); margin-top: 0; }
  .segment-card { background: var(--black-2); padding: 48px 28px; transition: background 0.4s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .segment-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--gold); transform: scaleX(0); transition: transform 0.4s; }
  .segment-card:hover { background: var(--black-3); }
  .segment-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .segment-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 52px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 20px; transition: color 0.4s; }
  .segment-card:hover .segment-num { color: rgba(201,168,76,0.22); }
  .segment-name { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .segment-en { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--gold-dark); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .segment-desc { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--white-dim); line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .segment-tags { margin-top: 20px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .tag { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--gold-dark); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); padding: 3px 8px; }

  /* Global */
  .map-intro { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; margin-bottom: 60px; align-items: end; }
  .map-desc { font-size: 14px; line-height: 2.2; color: var(--white-dim); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .regions-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
  .region-card { background: var(--black-2); padding: 36px 28px; transition: background 0.3s; }
  .region-card:hover { background: var(--black-3); }
  .region-title { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 18px; padding-bottom: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); }
  .region-loc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--white-dim); letter-spacing: 1px; padding-left: 12px; position: relative; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .region-loc::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 4px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold-dark); }

  /* Technology */
  .tech-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
  .tech-card { background: var(--black-2); padding: 52px 44px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: background 0.3s; }
  .tech-card:hover { background: var(--black-3); }
  .tech-card-label { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 5px; color: var(--gold-dark); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .tech-card-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .tech-card-desc { font-size: 13px; line-height: 2.2; color: var(--white-dim); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .tech-feat { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--white-dim); line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .tech-feat-dot { width: 20px; height: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--gold); font-size: 6px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .tech-bg-num { position: absolute; bottom: -20px; right: 20px; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 160px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.03); line-height: 1; pointer-events: none; }

  /* Leadership */
  .leadership-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
  .leader-card { background: var(--black-2); padding: 44px 36px; transition: background 0.3s; position: relative; }
  .leader-card::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
  .leader-card:hover { background: var(--black-3); }
  .leader-card:hover::after { opacity: 1; }
  .leader-role { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--gold-dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .leader-name { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 4px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
  .bio-item { display: flex; gap: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--white-dim); line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .bio-item::before { content: '·'; color: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Strategy */
  .strategy-pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1); }
  .pillar-card { background: var(--black-2); padding: 52px 32px; transition: background 0.3s; }
  .pillar-card:hover { background: var(--black-3); }
  .pillar-index { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 68px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.07); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .pillar-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .pillar-desc { font-size: 13px; line-height: 2; color: var(--white-dim); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }

  /* Footer */
  footer { background: var(--black-2); border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); padding: 80px 60px 40px; }
  .footer-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto 60px; padding-bottom: 60px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08); }
  .footer-logo-main { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 8px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .footer-logo-en { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 5px; color: var(--gold-dark); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .footer-motto { font-size: 14px; color: var(--white-dim); letter-spacing: 3px; font-weight: 300; }
  .footer-col-title { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); }
  .footer-links a { display: block; font-size: 12px; color: var(--white-dim); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 10px; transition: color 0.3s; }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  .footer-bottom { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .footer-copy { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.3); }
  .footer-tagline { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(201,168,76,0.3); letter-spacing: 4px; font-weight: 300; }

  /* Reveal */
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease; }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .d1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; } .d2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; } .d3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; } .d4 { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    nav, nav.scrolled { padding: 18px 30px; }
    .sec { padding: 80px 30px; }
    .sec-bg-inner { padding: 80px 30px; }
    .about-grid, .map-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .segments-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .regions-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .leadership-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .strategy-pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .segments-grid, .tech-grid, .leadership-grid, .strategy-pillars, .regions-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
    <div class="nav-logo-icon">豐</div>
    <div>
      <span class="nav-logo-cn">丰麒集团</span>
      <span class="nav-logo-en">FENGQI GROUP</span>
    </div>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">关于我们</a></li>
    <li><a href="#business">业务版块</a></li>
    <li><a href="#global">全球布局</a></li>
    <li><a href="#technology">科技平台</a></li>
    <li><a href="#leadership">管理团队</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">联系我们</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-corner tl"></div>
  <div class="hero-corner tr"></div>
  <div class="hero-corner bl"></div>
  <div class="hero-corner br"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">ESTABLISHED 2014 · HONG KONG</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title"><span>丰</span>麒<span>集</span>团</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">FENGQI GROUP LIMITED</p>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <p class="hero-tagline">农业全产业链数智化生态服务商</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <span>SCROLL</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about" class="sec">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">ABOUT US</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">关于<em>丰麒</em></h2>
    <div class="gold-line"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="about-text reveal d1">丰麒集团有限公司成立于2014年，深耕全球产业布局。集团在东南亚印尼投资建设物流产业园区，于非洲安哥拉布局农业产业园区，在南美古巴开发物流产业园区。</p>
      <p class="about-text reveal d2">2024年集团于香港设立投资公司，正式布局大中华区农业领域，以"双碳目标＋乡村振兴"为战略引擎，打造"农业科技创新＋跨境物流网络＋供应链数智化管理＋国际贸易服务"四位一体产业生态体系，着力推动农业绿色转型与全球化流通体系建设。</p>
      <div class="about-stats reveal d3">
        <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">10+</div><div class="stat-label">年全球运营经验</div></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">20+</div><div class="stat-label">全球城市布局</div></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">5</div><div class="stat-label">核心业务板块</div></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">36</div><div class="stat-label">项知识产权</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal d2">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-title">荣誉与资质</div>
        <div class="about-card-text">集团持有供应链及农业相关软件著作权共36项、多项实用新型专利在申，技术实力深厚。</div>
        <div class="honor-item">深圳市商业联合会副会长</div>
        <div class="honor-item">全国城市农贸中心联合会理事单位</div>
        <div class="honor-item">深圳市产业园区协会副会长单位（2025-2027）</div>
        <div class="honor-item">供应链相关软件著作权 18 项</div>
        <div class="honor-item">农业相关软件著作权 18 项</div>
        <div class="honor-item">农业相关实用新型专利 4 项在申</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- BUSINESS -->
<div class="sec-bg" id="business">
  <div class="sec-bg-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-label">BUSINESS SEGMENTS</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">五大<em>业务</em>板块</h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="segments-grid">
      <div class="segment-card reveal d1">
        <div class="segment-num">01</div>
        <div class="segment-name">丰麒农业</div>
        <div class="segment-en">FENGQI AGRICULTURE</div>
        <div class="segment-desc">以"木本源技术＋生态康养＋智慧农业"三驱发展，打造"可循环、高价值、全链条"农业生态经济标杆。依托EnzyLoop酶能循环生态饲育系统与R-AIoT智能优化平台，构建立体农业生态闭环。</div>
        <div class="segment-tags"><span class="tag">生态循环</span><span class="tag">智慧农业</span><span class="tag">文旅康养</span></div>
      </div>
